'''''Gordoon''''' was a group of three [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighters]]. Two of them carried [[Ore/Legends|ore]], the third carried [[Gold/Legends|gold]] and ore. They were present in the [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] [[Asteroid field|field]] during the raid of the Imperial convoy that involved the [[Delta-class DX-9 stormtrooper transport|Stormtrooper transport]] [[Raider (Delta-class DX-9 stormtrooper transport)|''Raider'']] that was attempting to steal food from the convoy and were likely destroyed.

